# ===============================
# MODULES
# ===============================

### List modules
GET {{baseUrl}}/modules
Accept: {{json}}

### Create module
POST {{baseUrl}}/modules
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "title": "Module Test",
  "position": 1,
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}"
}

### Get module by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/modules/{{moduleId}}
Accept: {{json}}


# ===============================
# LESSONS
# ===============================

### List lessons
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons
Accept: {{json}}

### List lessons by module
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons?moduleId={{moduleId}}
Accept: {{json}}

### Create lesson
POST {{baseUrl}}/lessons
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "title": "Lesson Test",
  "content": "Contenu de la leçon",
  "moduleId": "{{moduleId}}",
  "position": 1,
  "difficulty": "BEGINNER"
}

### Get lesson by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}
Accept: {{json}}
